@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rpfhri(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos((tmp + 0.07 + tmp + 0.62)))
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.98 - v1 + 0.71) / (v1 + 0.67 + v1 + 0.26)) - 0.98)
    v2 = (v1 * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.54) + (v0 + 0.87 - v1 + 0.92)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.42)) / (v2 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.76)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(0.99))
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
